Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.40,0:00:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.40,0:00:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基連總帥戰死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.95,0:00:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿·巴瓦·庫已全權
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.20,0:00:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移交給基希莉亞閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.70,0:00:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陰謀啊！基希莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.35,0:00:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦的雜魚們！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集結全艦以及全MS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs34\3c&H00ef877e}MS：Mobile Space Utility Instruments Tactical\N(戰術性泛用宇宙機動機械)的縮寫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.65,0:00:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我艦隊撤離此空域
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.40,0:00:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉，不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.10,0:00:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已下了撤退命令
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.85,0:00:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！卡多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的母艦多洛瓦被擊沉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.15,0:01:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多洛瓦？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.75,0:01:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的總帥基連閣下也逝世了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.90,0:01:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要撤離阿·巴瓦·庫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.70,0:01:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須活下去繼承總帥的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.25,0:01:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要我茍且偷生嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.95,0:01:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.41,0:01:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.25,0:01:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在要忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.90,0:01:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在手握活著才能得到的那份榮光為止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.00,0:01:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的性命就托付於我！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.85,0:01:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.45,0:01:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為一年戰爭中最大激戰的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.62,0:01:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿·巴瓦·庫一役後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.00,0:01:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球聯邦政府與ZION共和國
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.00,0:01:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs34\3c&H00ef877e}ZION：太空殖民地SIDE3獨立時取ZION作為國名，與聯邦對立
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.55,0:01:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,締結了終戰協定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那只意味著新一輪戰鬥的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.40,0:01:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)\fs60}GUNDAM 搶奪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.90,0:02:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這爛ZAKU！動作這麼遲鈍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.90,0:02:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs34\3c&H00ef877e}ZAKU：型號MS-05，最早開發投入實戰的MS\N一年戰爭中ZION的主力MS，並衍生出大量的型號
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟強化後的GM根本沒得比
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs34\3c&H00ef877e}GM：GUNDAM Massproduction的縮寫，型號RGM-79\N根據RX-78簡化再設計的量產機，聯邦MS的骨幹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏、吉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.90,0:02:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,採取第三陣形
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.00,0:02:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口氣幹掉它！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.65,0:02:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.58,0:02:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.20,0:02:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉斯少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有好好學過駕駛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得手了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！這是什麼推進力！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那背包對GM來說太笨重了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝在ZAKU上一定很配
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉斯，你逼緊GM
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面是殖民地殘骸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.85,0:03:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我繞到前面去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.30,0:03:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟得上就很不容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太、太快了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.50,0:04:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有搞錯，怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.30,0:04:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴寧格大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉斯機陷入殘骸無法動彈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.75,0:04:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要進行回收
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫且原地待機吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會再來回收
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了、瞭解…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.90,0:04:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴寧格大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.95,0:04:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GM的追加噴射器的數據不足
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.40,0:04:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距極限推力還有相當的餘力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿連中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.10,0:04:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是巴寧格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將追加噴射器的推力全開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.90,0:04:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續進行模擬戰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.30,0:04:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕沙洛夫大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.85,0:05:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有異常吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我擅自進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席那普斯艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係，巴普爾頓小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.05,0:05:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過從賈布羅到這幾乎都是海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定很悶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.35,0:05:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便同樣是海
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同地點的海流和顏色也會不斷變換
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.75,0:05:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，這是你第一次來地球吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.30,0:05:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快到澳大利亞大陸了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:05:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.05,0:06:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛經過了昔日的悉尼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今所見的海洋曾是一片陸地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是ZION的「不列顛作戰」造成的傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏就是殖民地的墜落痕跡？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大直徑達五百公里的彈坑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.95,0:06:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史上最大的人工坑穴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當於六萬MegaTon級的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為戰爭的代價
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傷痕也未免太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多少佐，來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是飛馬級
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.65,0:06:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很準時啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對聯邦而言似乎是少有的正經艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.70,0:06:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼叫U-COM
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs34\3c&H00ef877e}U-COM：以聯邦軍Ⅷ級潛艇為艦身設計的潛艇\N可裝載MS及擁有良好的秘密作戰能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是Walfisch
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍的飛馬級確認
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.80,0:07:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星塵作戰開始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.70,0:07:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,92
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,93
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,94
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.55,0:07:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,95
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,96
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賈布羅花了不少錢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能撥少許來這裏就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.65,0:07:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.81,0:07:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛馬級的嗎？大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是白色基地的改良型的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…搭載機是GUNDAM類型？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾時能去看看？大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，讓我去調查清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待明早的作戰簡報吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.85,0:07:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天辛苦了，解散
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.00,0:07:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉斯，你想一直趴下去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.65,0:08:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉斯，它著陸了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.90,0:08:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏！開慢點！宏！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你一起總能遇上一些有趣的意外，真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…去哪裏？宏兄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.93,0:08:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.40,0:08:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.74,0:08:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.75,0:08:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的，和你一起不會覺得悶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.60,0:09:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,申報
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席那普斯大佐以下乘員211名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.35,0:09:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭載強襲登陸艦阿爾比昂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運載二架新型MS按時到達
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.46,0:09:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了，大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.40,0:09:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曼涅裏准將
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我申請立即簽發核儲備庫的開封許可
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是由賈布羅帶來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,許可書及由明天起測試項目的一覽表
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,測試機師由你來挑選
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檔案已準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你酌情安排吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以期萬全
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM有兩架！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.80,0:10:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧啊，吉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.75,0:10:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs34\3c&H00ef877e}Core Fighter：核心戰鬥機\N確保駕駛員的安全和回收戰鬥數據所用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這架裝了Core Fighter！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架也很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.75,0:10:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個重裝甲…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不尋常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.30,0:10:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實不尋常啊，那位小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是基地的人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.22,0:10:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿納海姆的人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.55,0:10:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不、敝人是測試機師恰克·吉斯少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，原來是擔任測試機師的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.60,0:11:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是系統工程師 妮娜·巴普爾頓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.50,0:11:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才要請你多指教呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是同期的宏·浦木少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏！是妮娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妮娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿納海姆的系統工程師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.60,0:11:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請、請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很怕羞，對美人沒有抵抗力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.17,0:11:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅對美人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.60,0:11:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM正在維護中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.56,0:11:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要參觀的話日後再聯絡你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就和我聯絡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天幾點結束工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.40,0:11:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須定好約會的時間才行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.06,0:11:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去喝啤酒如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.70,0:11:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？歐比爾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊檢查OK了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒其他事的話，我想去散散步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊！辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.65,0:11:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散步…這裏什麼都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.05,0:11:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我們這些生活在宇宙的人而言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.85,0:11:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球上的一切都很新奇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:12:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，晚霞！一定是去看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.50,0:12:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多是時候了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.40,0:12:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶你去個看晚霞的最佳場所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.93,0:12:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，我看不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下嘛，宏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說等一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏！你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太纏人是很討人嫌的，小子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲，喲…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.95,0:12:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約會？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.25,0:12:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.50,0:12:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡到抓著我手不放的話就陪你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚霞或是啤酒都行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離這還有一小時行程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blau Engel呼叫Walfisch
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:12:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是Walfisch
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:13:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blau Engel很順利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切照預定行事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.50,0:13:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Walfisch瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南極條約簽署以來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:13:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏還是第一次開啟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.45,0:14:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真希望眼前這扇門繼續緊閉著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.26,0:14:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歐姆中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切記不要大意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只是個邊境基地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.30,0:14:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,測試機師的話個個都有一流的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.15,0:14:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您放心！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.80,0:14:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐身負重任
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.90,0:14:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請一定小心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫歐比爾吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有大尉的制服了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了，我也不會因此而改變什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.90,0:14:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待各位的活躍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GM換裝的背包
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.40,0:14:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推力好強
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.00,0:14:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腿部的震動吸收裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.50,0:14:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超高度落下也有充分耐力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:15:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GM已經如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.10,0:15:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型機就更令人期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.55,0:15:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型機令人期待是什麼意思？中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.20,0:15:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿連中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說過新型機的機師還未定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.50,0:15:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏的機師稱得上王牌的是大尉您
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想這已是定局了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.80,0:15:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想駕駛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.65,0:15:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成天對著討厭的ZAKU…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.80,0:15:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎喲，ZAKU也是好機體哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.30,0:15:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.28,0:15:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阿納海姆的系統工程師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.18,0:15:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜·巴普爾頓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.10,0:15:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿納海姆的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為部下的無禮向你致歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.15,0:15:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是指揮測試機師的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴寧格大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.80,0:15:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡克斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.95,0:15:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失禮了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是摩拉·巴席特中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由賈布羅來此負責機械整備的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.93,0:15:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後請多多指教，大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.75,0:15:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，可以與您同席嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:15:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請坐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.80,0:16:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型機的動力似乎提升相當多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背包的測試已經完成了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.10,0:16:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天把它試裝在改良型GM上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.01,0:16:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動力提升了好幾級
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.12,0:16:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說新型機要從這基地裏挑選測試機師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想找什麼樣的機師呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能透露一下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對本公司來說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是能發揮出新型機最高性能的機師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便是最受歡迎的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩拉，該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.65,0:16:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.45,0:16:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.95,0:16:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才想說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.30,0:16:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於用舊型機訓練的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.15,0:16:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能將新型機的性能發揮到什麼程度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.55,0:16:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點擔心而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.05,0:16:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要胡蘿蔔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.75,0:16:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，打攪一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.40,0:16:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參觀的話明天以後再說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從GUNDAM的反應速度快了0.5秒左右來看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出力提高了三成吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.15,0:17:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GM連三分之二也發揮不出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那重裝甲的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用的是對核兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.95,0:17:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩上的火箭炮是戰術核裝備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.16,0:17:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是想證實這點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.98,0:17:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是機師吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好敏銳的觀察力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但誰知道技術方面又如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.50,0:17:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來晚了，抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阿納海姆公司的歐比爾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.69,0:17:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？晚霞美不美？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.99,0:17:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日出也很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今晚得早點睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:17:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.25,0:17:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.46,0:18:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟如此鬆懈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦到哪裏都是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟和這樣的傢伙們打到現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安裝完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣算是告一段落了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴普爾頓小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.45,0:18:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天仍有很多事要麻煩你，拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.60,0:18:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？在做什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的兩位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏應該禁止進入的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.85,0:19:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1號機這邊只裝備機槍彈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.10,0:19:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道現正在裝備彈頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.50,0:19:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以別來礙事，快點給我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.20,0:19:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她如果不那麼帶刺就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是死心吧，吉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.10,0:19:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說，她討厭你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.10,0:19:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點我也知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.61,0:19:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去陪我喝悶酒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.50,0:19:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，再看一會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.96,0:19:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好傷心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:19:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起的MS
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.86,0:20:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也這樣認為
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.45,0:20:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火箭炮已裝備好彈頭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.25,0:20:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，我就來試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.57,0:20:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人真是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次又想搞什麼新花樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.60,0:20:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.90,0:20:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請關掉艙門下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.50,0:20:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.65,0:20:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能聽到吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.75,0:20:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:21:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來人啊，誰來阻止2號機！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.60,0:21:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.30,0:21:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木少尉？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木少尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去叫別人來，以你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.62,0:21:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是機師！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.35,0:21:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在裝彈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.75,0:21:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法立即出動的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請快點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.25,0:21:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2號機的機師，你能聽到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.95,0:21:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上下來的話罪責尚輕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在馬上從2號機上下來！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這架機體和核彈頭我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.90,0:21:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了ZION的復興！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.85,0:21:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZION？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.90,0:21:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舷格納庫內壁破損
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.90,0:22:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,損傷狀況確認中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.90,0:22:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長，格納庫有聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.40,0:22:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2號機被自稱是ZION的人奪走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.00,0:22:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2號機被奪走了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.25,0:22:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導彈群接近
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.73,0:22:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離一萬二千！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.95,0:22:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.80,0:22:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舷引擎中彈！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.25,0:22:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出力下降
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.45,0:22:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各部報告破損部位
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.35,0:22:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查出導彈發射位置
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.02,0:22:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.01,0:22:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米諾夫斯基粒子散佈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.76,0:22:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.10,0:22:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.00,0:22:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今ZION還想幹什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.50,0:22:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席那普斯艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.70,0:22:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請阻止1號機
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.30,0:22:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1號機怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.15,0:22:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,測試機師浦木少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.94,0:22:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算乘坐著去制止2號機
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.15,0:22:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快裝備好實彈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.84,0:22:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡克斯，吉斯，快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.36,0:23:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是模擬戰！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.50,0:23:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心應付！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.66,0:23:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.20,0:23:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.25,0:23:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉，是ZION
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.80,0:23:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZION把裝備核彈頭的2號機奪走了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.30,0:23:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.22,0:23:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZION？！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.70,0:23:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙又想發動戰爭嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.00,0:23:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要殺死多少人才罷手！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.80,0:23:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.60,0:23:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.80,0:23:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.50,0:23:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZAKU…嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.10,0:23:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為聯邦所用了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.00,0:23:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣子實在不忍目睹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.70,0:24:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多少佐！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.10,0:24:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓋利嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.00,0:24:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰成功
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.30,0:24:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.15,0:24:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想從這離開！
